::Autofire::

Autofire growls as shots hit him armored chest, the Predacon gaining 
altitude. He looks down, the bots on the ground looking like tiny ants. They 
were really pissing him off. Mech fluid was leaking through the cracks in his 
armor, and his optics were running a bit low on power. He takes out a charge, 
dropping it onto the bots on the ground, firing at Terrorsaur with all three 
of his guns.

He growls as shots from the Autoguns nearly hit him, gliding down to Adrax.

"The battle seems to have evened out, lets get out of here," he tells the 
other bot, ready for further attacks.
